# Workforges Frontend Roadmap

The frontend will host the UI for all ERP modules.

---

## Phase 0 — Foundation (Current)
- [ ] Polished dashboard UI
- [ ] Responsive layout
- [ ] Component structure ready
- [ ] Dummy screens for CRM, Sales, Inventory, Accounting, HRM

---

## Phase 1 — CRM + Sales
- [ ] CRM → Leads table page
- [ ] CRM → Lead details view
- [ ] Sales → Quotations table
- [ ] Form to create quotation (dummy API)

---

## Phase 2 — User System + Dashboard
- [ ] Login page (with backend later)
- [ ] Protected routes (dashboard)
- [ ] Multi-company + multi-user UI
- [ ] Dashboard KPIs + charts

---

## Phase 3 — Full UI Integration
- [ ] Inventory screens
- [ ] Accounting screens
- [ ] HRM screens
- [ ] Settings / Profile screen

